Package: fcnet
Title: Functional Connectivity Analysis Tools for fMRI Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Shijing", "Zhou", , "shijingz@uoregon.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7053-0953"))
Description: Tools for analyzing network-level functional connectivity from 
    fMRI data using parcellated brain atlases. Loads connectivity matrices from 
    the CONN toolbox, extracts network and ROI groupings, and calculates 
    within-network, between-network, and user-defined connectivity metrics. 
    Supports flexible ROI definitions and custom network assignments. Optimized 
    for the Schaefer atlas but adaptable to other parcellation schemes.
